itunes:subtitle: PANTS with Kate Moennig & Leisha Hailey.Actress Erin Daniels, known and adored for playing tennis player Dana Fairbanks on The L Word, joins PANTS for much merriment and reminiscing.Alice and Dana: a prelude to the love story.
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Actress Erin Daniels, known and adored for playing tennis player Dana Fairbanks on The L Word, joins PANTS for much merriment and reminiscing.

Together they plot her return to the show...


Alice and Dana. A prelude to the love story.


"We miss the shit outta you."


Edited and produced in the UK by Rachel Shelley.
